channel.description:

Need helP!

item.dc:creator: @Mrquarter Mrquarter
item.description:
@Mrquarter wrote:

[i]Ok. Copy your compile.bat and paste it. Name it Endserver. Then edit it to have this inside it

tskill java /a

Now click that. Run that and it will close all servers. Then you can runserver.[/i]
